div.p: Millennial-scale structure in notched δ 18O pf compared to δ 18O cave. a Notched U1429 δ 18O pf on the cave-based age model. b Expanded 20–80 ka interval with millennial-scale Dansgaard–Oeschger (DO) and Heinrich events numbered. c Expanded 100–210 ka interval. d Expanded 250–340 ka interval showing structure not previously resolved in δ 18O cave
